    {
      "role": "user",
      "content": "that makes sense. it seems like a lot of these small shops might actually have to shut down if they cant handle the costs. do you think the government is being realistic about how much these regs are going to hurt local economies, or is this more about hitting specific climate targets regardless of the economic fallout?",
